title: *PATREON PREVIEW* AMA After Dark
description:
The Core Four, plus special guest R. Kelly, link up for a podcast pregame ahead of Throwing Fits’ inaugural Patreon soiree. Welcome to an absolutely blasted Ask Me Anything courtesy of our friends at home leaving 5 star Apple reviews. We’re answering all your burning questions: What are our favorite hills to die on? Where would we relocate? How do you cop jawnz on a budget? What are some fashion tips for big boys? What’s Chef’s origin story? How do you upgrade your media diet? What’s life like as TF vs. FU? Are Jimmy and Larry actually friends? All that and much more on this Patreon-exclusive boys only edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
